EVALUATIVE Chirality Framework  Evaluation Systems v1.1

#######
This is a framework for meta-learning and knowledge generation. 
When expressed through its modalities it says: {problem statement} → Systematic → Process → Epistemic → Process → Epistemic → Alethic → Epistemic → Alethic → {consistency check} 

This evaluation is of the coherence of that modality stack in the application of a general learning and knowledge generation paradigm. 
If it does, then the components of the Chirality Framework can be used to produce valid knowledge, provided the implementation work.
While that is a big "IF" and further evaluation is needed, this is the core evaluation basis.  
If the foundation is good, you can build.
